ing.</span></p>','<p>&nbsp;<span class=\"s1\">We had the structural engineer redesign the steel at street level in order to accommodate the truck loading. This allowed us to use the street level for the truss erection of granite panels in the atrium, concrete placement at the loading dock, and truck deliveries, for items such as spray fireproofing.</span></p>','2016-04-11 16:02:41','2016-04-11 16:02:41'),(16,'App\\Study',4,1,'analysis','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">This scenario is perhaps one of the most common issues associated with modern, urban, construction projects. Even the simplest of buildings can become a logistical nightmare when there is a lack of space to mobilize the project. When one is faced with an issue such as this, it can prove to be quite costly in terms of time and money if the situation is not dealt with in the appropriate fashion. This case is a perfect example of how one might overcome the limitations set by a congested jobsite. Not every issue can be solved by the construction manager alone. More often than not, the CM will find it beneficial to consult their subcontractor, design team, and even owners in regards to more specialized issues. In this particular instance, the mobilization was significantly facilitated as a result of assistance from the project&rsquo;s structural subcontractor.&nbsp;</span></p>','<p>&nbsp;<span class=\"s1\">This scenario is perhaps one of the most common issues associated with modern, urban, construction projects. Even the simplest of buildings can become a logistical nightmare when there is a lack of space to mobilize the project. When one is faced with an issue such as this, it can prove to be quite costly in terms of time and money if the situation is not dealt with in the appropriate fashion. This case is a perfect example of how one might overcome the limitations set by a congested jobsite. Not every issue can be solved by the construction manager alone. More often than not, the CM will find it beneficial to consult their subcontractor, design team, and even owners in regards to more specialized issues. In this particular instance, the mobilization was significantly facilitated as a result of assistance from the project&rsquo;s structural subcontractor.&nbsp;</span></p>','2016-04-11 16:02:41','2016-04-11 16:02:41'),(17,'App\\Study',4,1,'excerpt','&nbsp;\r\nWe had limited room for mobilizing our workforce on a tight construction site in Boston....','&nbsp;We had limited room for mobilizing our workforce on a tight construction site in Boston....','2016-04-11 16:02:41','2016-04-11 16:02:41'),(18,'App\\Study',4,1,'delivery_method',NULL,'','2016-04-11 16:02:41','2016-04-11 16:02:41'),(19,'App\\Study',4,1,'estimated_schedule',NULL,'','2016-04-11 16:02:41','2016-04-11 16:02:41'),(20,'App\\Study',4,1,'contract_value',NULL,'','2016-04-11 16:02:41','2016-04-11 16:02:41'),(21,'App\\Study',4,1,'market_sector',NULL,'','2016-04-11 16:02:41','2016-04-11 16:02:41'),(22,'App\\Study',4,1,'topic',NULL,'','2016-04-11 16:02:41','2016-04-11 16:02:41'),(23,'App\\Study',4,1,'location',NULL,'','2016-04-11 16:02:41','2016-04-11 16:02:41'),(24,'App\\Study',11,1,'delivery_method',NULL,'','2016-04-11 16:12:39','2016-04-11 16:12:39'),(25,'App\\Study',11,1,'estimated_schedule',NULL,'','2016-04-11 16:12:39','2016-04-11 16:12:39'),(26,'App\\Study',11,1,'contract_value',NULL,'','2016-04-11 16:12:39','2016-04-11 16:12:39'),(27,'App\\Study',11,1,'market_sector',NULL,'','2016-04-11 16:12:39','2016-04-11 16:12:39'),(28,'App\\Study',11,1,'topic',NULL,'','2016-04-11 16:12:39','2016-04-11 16:12:39'),(29,'App\\Study',11,1,'location',NULL,'','2016-04-11 16:12:39','2016-04-11 16:12:39'),(30,'App\\Study',10,1,'problem','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">We were awarded a contract to provide construction management services to a University working on an existing building. The work was to be performed on the 4th floor with classrooms and research labs below. The schedule 